"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-09-03-molly-thompson-smith-fire-lit-olympic-redemption-21538750\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Pariswas a whirlwind but what a privilege it was to be a part of it.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 68, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whirlwind\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 20}, {\"ngram\": \"what a privilege\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 61}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very much enjoying being home again but my the last few weeks are finally starting to sink in and I am realising that I am officially an Olympian.\", \"from\": 69, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999826636669, \"rank\": 1.7335695685067886e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last few weeks\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AnOlympic Gamesis a pretty special event.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AnOlympic Gamesis\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty special event\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With most of the world's attention set on one place for two weeks, everything feels a lot more intense and exaggerated.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's attention\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"one place\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly it's not just the climbing community watching us compete!\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the climbing community\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a hard thing to process while I was out in France but it feels as if I have woken up from a dream now that I am back in Sheffield.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8011248595460322, \"rank\": 0.24823528568832504, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.9999999099782184, \"rank\": 8.908713973103477e-08, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard thing\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went there not really knowing what to expect and it certainly beat whatever I could have imagined.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' village really had everything you could need or want for a home from home; a post office, supermarket, hairdressers and more than enoughcoffeeshops to keep the thousands of athletes staying there caffeinated.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes' village\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"a home\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"a post office\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"supermarket\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"hairdressers\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"enoughcoffeeshops\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the thousands\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our climbing cohort really contributed to the success of Team GB in Paris, with my teenage team-mate Toby Roberts bringing home our first Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999998389764119, \"rank\": 1.6031289773517678e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9999999962001311, \"rank\": 3.451462346354161e-09, \"text\": \"Toby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our climbing cohort\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"our first Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamish McArthur and Erin McNeice's strong performances and fifth-place finishes on top of Toby's gold showed the depth of talent we have in this country.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"score\": 0.9999961483200931, \"rank\": 3.8516947883243645e-06, \"text\": \"Erin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9999999962001311, \"rank\": 3.451462346354161e-09, \"text\": \"Toby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fifth-place finishes\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"the depth\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performance in Paris was a statement to the world from UK climbing.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9937010817738479, \"rank\": 0.006337874293698143, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The performance\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was amazing to see how much diversity there was among teams and I really enjoyed seeing so many different cultures and races around the village.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how much diversity\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different cultures\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the climbing community is incredibly friendly, it still very much lacks diversity and so it was personally a very inspiring environment to be a part of and I enjoyed a chance to step out of the climbing bubble and not feel different for once.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the climbing community\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"a very inspiring environment\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the climbing bubble\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Climbing clearly left its mark after Tokyo, as every session at Le Bourget was sold out and the crowd supplied a great atmosphere throughout the competition.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1741, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7736485687126358, \"rank\": 0.2925370639177529, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Bourget\", \"score\": 0.9809335090241077, \"rank\": 0.01943708803965738, \"text\": \"Le Bourget\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Bourget\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Bourget\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Climbing\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"its mark\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"every session\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"a great atmosphere\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really exciting to see such appetite for our sport and I really think this is only the beginning.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such appetite\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"only the beginning\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a more personal level, however, the competition did not go as well as I had hoped.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more personal level\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately I broke a toe a few weeks before Paris, so my prep for the event was far from ideal.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a toe\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"my prep\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had my fair share of injuries and I did my best to work around this one but not being able to wear a climbing shoe or boulder for the month leading up to the competition was a big obstacle to overcome.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fair share\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"a climbing shoe\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"boulder\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"a big obstacle\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boulder round was tricky - as I knew it would be in the circumstances.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The boulder round\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"the circumstances\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried my best on a set of climbs that exposed my weaknesses and poor preparation in the month before but sadly I finished in a disappointing 19th place.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"climbs\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"my weaknesses\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"poor preparation\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointing 19th place\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had been on a long journey to qualify for the Olympics and put a lot of time into improving my bouldering so it was frustrating not to be able to show the progress I had made over the years.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long journey\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"my bouldering\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"the progress\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With my score from the boulder round being so low I knew there wasn't much I could do to improve my final rank, so two days later I pulled my shoes on again for the lead round determined to go out and enjoy myself.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my score\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"the boulder round\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"my final rank\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoes\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead round\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I climbed well on the lead route but did not quite show what I am capable of in that discipline.\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead route\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"that discipline\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with the end of that six-minute opportunity to showcase my climbing, came the end of my Olympic competition.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"that six-minute opportunity\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"my climbing\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"my Olympic competition\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a lot of my family and friends in the crowd proud of me for just being there, I chose to celebrate both my ninth-place finish on the lead route and the whole journey which started as an inspired little girl watching the Games on TV.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"both my ninth-place finish\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead route\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole journey\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspired little girl\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a long journey to get to Paris and I am definitely feeling tired after 11 years of international competition.\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long journey\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"11 years\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"international competition\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this Olympic Games lit a small fire inside me and the idea of redemption in Los Angeles in 2028 is bouncing around my head.\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3654, \"end\": 3665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999990986908, \"rank\": 8.683616649972873e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"a small fire\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"redemption\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after reflecting on my Paris experience my focus quickly switched to last week's European Championships and our national championships this coming weekend.\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3730, \"end\": 3735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3788, \"end\": 3810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9301349237604251, \"rank\": 0.07507020419716207, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3746}, {\"ngram\": \"my focus\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3755}, {\"ngram\": \"our national championships\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Paris closing the door on the combined format, I am really excited to get back to focusing on my preferred discipline of lead.\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3869, \"end\": 3874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.038290028837439e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"the combined format\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3914}, {\"ngram\": \"my preferred discipline\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"lead\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 3994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's fair to say, I may just have the Olympic bug.\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic bug\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Molly Thompson-Smith is an ambassador of The North Face - Never Stop Exploring ArrowMORE:Victor Osimhen includes Arsenal and Chel